---
import ScreenWrapper from "./ui/ScreenWrapper.astro";
---

<section class="mb-20 animate-on-load fade-in-up mt-20">
    <ScreenWrapper class="px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-[6rem]">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center mb-10 gap-4">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[#222222]">Work History</h2>
            <a href="/files/lowkeydev.docx" download class="bg-[#222222] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15V3m0 12l-4-4m4 4l4-4M2 17l.621 2.485A2 2 0 0 0 4.561 21h14.878a2 2 0 0 0 1.94-1.515L22 17"/></svg>
                Download CV
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-8">
            <!-- Current Role: Gainset Trading Academy -->
            <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-gray-200">
                <div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-blue-500 border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:justify-between md:items-center mb-2">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#222222]">Fullstack Developer</h3>
                        <span class="text-sm text-blue-600 font-medium bg-blue-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full w-fit mt-2 md:mt-0">Present</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-[#7b7b7b] font-medium mb-4">Gainset Trading Academy • Remote</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-4 text-[#7b7b7b] space-y-2">
                        <li>Developed and maintained web applications for desktop and mobile platforms.</li>
                        <li>Improved software efficiency by identifying and fixing bugs pre-deployment.</li>
                        <li>Refactored legacy code for performance and modern standards.</li>
                        <li>Collaborated with cross-functional teams on Agile-based sprints.</li>
                        <li>Designed and implemented user-friendly, responsive interfaces.</li>
                        <li>Optimized application performance through code reviews and refactoring.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-[#7b7b7b] text-xs rounded-md">React.js</span>
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-[#7b7b7b] text-xs rounded-md">Next.js</span>
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-[#7b7b7b] text-xs rounded-md">Node.js</span>
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-[#7b7b7b] text-xs rounded-md">Express.js</span>
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-[#7b7b7b] text-xs rounded-md">MongoDB</span>
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-[#7b7b7b] text-xs rounded-md">PostgreSQL</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Current Role: Tadexpress -->
            <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-gray-200">
                <div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-blue-500 border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:justify-between md:items-center mb-2">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#222222]">Fullstack Developer (Team Lead)</h3>
                        <span class="text-sm text-blue-600 font-medium bg-blue-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full w-fit mt-2 md:mt-0">Present</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-[#7b7b7b] font-medium mb-4">Tadexpress • Remote</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-4 text-[#7b7b7b] space-y-2">
                        <li>Managed backend server hosting and DevOps infrastructure, ensuring high availability and security.</li>
                        <li>Developed, maintained, and secured backend server for website and applications.</li>
                        <li>Improved software efficiency by identifying and fixing bugs pre-deployment.</li>
                        <li>Refactored legacy code for performance and modern standards.</li>
                        <li>Collaborated with cross-functional teams on Agile-based sprints.</li>
                        <li>Designed and implemented user-friendly, responsive interfaces.</li>
                        <li>Optimized application performance through code reviews and refactoring.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-[#7b7b7b] text-xs rounded-md">React.js</span>
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-[#7b7b7b] text-xs rounded-md">Next.js</span>
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-[#7b7b7b] text-xs rounded-md">Node.js</span>
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-[#7b7b7b] text-xs rounded-md">Express.js</span>
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-[#7b7b7b] text-xs rounded-md">MongoDB</span>
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-[#7b7b7b] text-xs rounded-md">PostgreSQL</span>
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-[#7b7b7b] text-xs rounded-md">DevOps</span>
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-[#7b7b7b] text-xs rounded-md">Server Management</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Previous Role: CT0 -->
            <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-gray-200">
                <div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-gray-300 border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:justify-between md:items-center mb-2">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#222222]">CTO</h3>
                        <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium bg-gray-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full w-fit mt-2 md:mt-0">2025 - 2025</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-[#7b7b7b] font-medium mb-4">BlackSolvent • Remote</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-4 text-[#7b7b7b] space-y-2">
                        <li>Led the technical vision and execution of the company’s product development roadmap.</li>
                        <li>Architected and deployed full-stack web solutions using the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express, React, Node.js).</li>
                        <li>Oversaw code quality, team workflows, and sprint planning in line with Agile methodologies.</li>
                        <li>Built reusable front-end components and integrated REST APIs to enhance platform scalability.</li>
                        <li>Mentored junior developers and established best practices for clean, maintainable code.</li>
                        <li>Collaborated with the CEO and cross-functional teams to align technology initiatives with business goals.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </ScreenWrapper>
</section>
